{"tid":762131,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"EE R&D狗 走定唔走? 人生交叉點","createTime":"2018-07-31T04:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T04:01:29.000Z","uid":172726,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0869231ea99ce4051765bf53542ed28c8737dc","tid":762131,"uid":172726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"30出頭, 工作環境遇到d變化, 開始唸好多野<br />\n做緊某類設備R&amp;D, 平時寫下program畫下circuit (embedded system), 技術比較low-end果種<br />\n畢業到依家幫公司做左一個大project, 埋尾階段+準備開下一個product<br />\n再加上依家個product唔係好高profit (公司有其他非自家product好賺少少)<br />\n公司同我自己都好似無motivation專心搞新product<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n年頭同公司交帶底所有舊job資料, 準備隨時走人, 但半年間見過兩三份工都offer唔係太好, 搵緊30k唔想搵得少過呢個數, 養唔到家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到依家想走又唔想走<br />\n走左, 又怕搵辛苦+low pay<br />\n唔走, 又怕d技術跟唔到市場, 過多兩年先再搵工都比人嫌你老<br />\n1516左半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 驚會屈到有病<br />\n有無過來人可以分享下?<br />\n<br />\n講多少少backgorund:<br />\n自己在公司有一小部份share, 原因只係當年入職的甜頭, 未見過值d乜錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本早兩年有一team 5個人做R&amp;D, 其中一個蝗經常唔聽話, 自從比我屌走左之後條team另外兩個本地人都走埋 (相信只係offer原因+小許人事原因), 自此R&amp;D再無請新人, 公司的大project都幾乎停晒<br />\n彈性上班+有房坐, 間接地講係公司判左個project比我做 (係幾爽架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) , 所以同出面office幫人地打工, 我自己覺得呢樣轉變係最難接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而且準備要小朋友, 唔想份工太困身<br />\n另外公司腦細多, 意見多, 收到風公司業務好似出左d問題, 成日話拆夥乜乜乜, 管理又唔係好好, 半年間走左幾個開國功臣, 亦都係我怕有一日公司會訓低而想走的原因"},{"pid":"18aad3cf35250bd91b9282ddf08a40a91267e0d1","tid":762131,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"走<br />\n而家先30歲<br />\n唔走邊捱到咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eababaa23b4313c0c5df342f8a458be92cdd4fa","tid":762131,"uid":177272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"再報到幾間公司睇下會唔會有再好啲既offer 先再睇走唔走 出到去搵唔翻3k就仆乖了"},{"pid":"6a81729fd7f580e417040747a43cf3ab39daf3e3","tid":762131,"uid":172726,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3eababaa23b4313c0c5df342f8a458be92cdd4fa","tid":762131,"uid":177272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:22:23.000Z","msg":"再報到幾間公司睇下會唔會有再好啲既offer 先再睇走唔走 出到去搵唔翻3k就仆乖了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"年頭問左風水佬都係咁講<br />\n<br />\nBTW出去搵工先發現自己以前做D野太過專, 要搵返同一範好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5289cf531c2b33fdf4120bd289cdc618bdb78244","tid":762131,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"ee 狗有冇咩field 前途好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 讀緊ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51861d268b49db15a65276bbdacd824697162582","tid":762131,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5289cf531c2b33fdf4120bd289cdc618bdb78244","tid":762131,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:10:00.000Z","msg":"ee 狗有冇咩field 前途好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 讀緊ee<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T14:12:30.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n利申揸緊兜"},{"pid":"4c0bc7916096335a184f8c238c77741fce92a8e6","tid":762131,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51861d268b49db15a65276bbdacd824697162582","tid":762131,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5289cf531c2b33fdf4120bd289cdc618bdb78244","tid":762131,"uid":68646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime